Text: NYISO digital certificate noticeMarket Participants Please help the NYISO clean house so we can start our next year of operations with an uptodate database of active digital certificate holders You may receive multiple copies of this messages if so it indicates you have multiple certificates No action is needed in this case Please notify me of persons who may have had a certificate but have left your company or have other responsibilities within your company such that they no longer need or use their certificate Thank you Pete Morrison
